{"tid":514792,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【恥笑】 黃賓穎：「其實MV片頭當中兩隻喪屍係林師傑同周志康！」","createTime":"2017-12-30T22:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T10:16:24.000Z","uid":152123,"like":249,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"76e03bd92ff795db5f56f3987cae58c79e7a461a","tid":514792,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T22:14:37.000Z","msg":"【勁歌總選】TVB五小花為頒獎禮採排　爆《到此一遊》MV洗過百萬[img]assets/faces/xm/clown.png[/img] <br />\n<br />\n《2017年度勁歌金曲頒獎典禮》將於明晚舉行，今日中午在將軍澳電視城一廠進行綵排。而焦點自然落在馮盈盈、黃心穎、蔡思貝、張寶兒和邵珮詩五位TVB小花身上，皆因昨晚「See See TVB」的Facebook專頁發佈了五女翻唱胡鴻鈞《到此一遊》的MV，不足一日已得到近30萬觀看次數，今次TVB攻向年青人市場的確成功。而今次的MV當中，不論場景、服裝、舞步，以至鏡頭運用也跟足韓風，如此大製作，實是TVB的罕見例子。<br />\n<br />\n今日《香港01》訪問五位小花時，感激製作團隊之餘，馮盈盈更大爆：「消息人士話呢個MV過百萬！包括拍攝器材、場地同埋特技化妝。」<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃心穎透露：「其實MV片頭當中兩隻喪屍係林師傑同周志康，佢哋個特技化妝要七個鐘先搞得掂，嗰度洗費都唔少。所以我哋好多謝師傑同阿康，雖然佢哋出鏡唔係太多，不過都用咗好多時間去參與。</span></span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/e35/24175400_148729045852194_8644151931272429568_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F24175400_148729045852194_8644151931272429568_n.jpg&h=ea6316d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據知今次的女版《到此一遊》是TVB有史以來最貴的MV製作，連製作團隊也是外判的電影Crew負責拍攝，單是場景已有六個，當中包括了愉景灣的教堂、香港首席紋身師Gabe的工作室等等，部份場景更是要特色搭建，難怪製作水準這樣高，而製作費亦如此高昂。<br />\n<br />\n老老實實，重溫原版胡鴻鈞《到此一遊》的MV，似乎星夢也未及今次女版的MV重本製作。雖然胡鴻鈞的MV也是特意飛到台灣拍攝，不過整個MV大部分場景也集中在私家車廂及廢車場中。最貴大概也是MV中，胡鴻鈞駕駛的寶馬了，屈指一算，MV當中出現的寶馬，一架二手分分鐘也只是十多萬，加上其他製作費、機票、酒店，分分鐘五十萬都唔洗。雖然最近胡鴻鈞憑石敢當一角大受歡迎，不過與五小花比較下，難免有點失色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/145120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F145120&d=%2BZXaqsG7MrZkzdzQz3wCy9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2d546eb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/145120</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/061024_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F061024_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=2f17e9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/061033_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F061033_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7bdb9495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/061045_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F061045_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b7776f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/061057_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F061057_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1d10cc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>真係好棋都好過做喪屍 起碼見樣</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.cmoneyhome.com/upload/article_cover/original/5109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmoneyhome.com%2Fupload%2Farticle_cover%2Foriginal%2F5109.jpg&h=837c2953&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fd8517275140716a88bb020f9e86d9c8c06e3fe","tid":514792,"uid":72943,"like":243,"dislike":2,"score":241,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T22:42:39.000Z","msg":"邊撚到成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高成本版ffx"},{"pid":"9c22039fc21a014f9ebed04b8b4d75dc93a1a732","tid":514792,"uid":21028,"like":128,"dislike":3,"score":125,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T22:47:17.000Z","msg":"成首歌同個mv<br />\n有乜大關係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢洗千萬都唔明個mv講乜"},{"pid":"699c4fd659a11870a9f8a7